+{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_0149uc7CAiL4ysvf7yrU6L7G","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"No checkpoint found. The project is set up with TypeScript, Vitest, and ESLint, but `src/` is empty. This is a non-interactive environment, so I'll use Autopilot mode.\n\nNon-interactive mode: using Autopilot. The requirements are well-specified in the task description, so the design decisions are straightforward. Let me quickly make the key design decisions and move to implementation.\n\n**Key design decisions (autopilot):**\n\n1. **Architecture**: Single `Spreadsheet` class with internal formula parser, dependency graph, and topological sort for reactive updates. All in `src/` directory.\n2. **Formula parsing**: Recursive descent parser for arithmetic expressions, cell references, ranges, function calls, comparisons, and string literals.\n3. **Dependency tracking**: Directed graph mapping each cell to its dependencies. On cell set, rebuild deps, detect cycles via DFS, then topologically sort and recompute affected cells.\n4. **File structure**: `src/index.ts` (Spreadsheet class + export), `src/parser.ts` (formula parser), `src/types.ts` (shared types). Tests in `src/__tests__/`.\n5. **Circular reference detection**: DFS cycle detection before accepting a formula. Throw error if cycle detected.\n\nNow let me invoke the TDD skill for implementation."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":993,"cache_read_input_tokens":22359,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":993},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"6a5d19eb-4325-4e27-b2c6-05578ec9e92d","uuid":"cc1adb2e-1d4d-405b-8504-35bf30ab8cd1"}
